## 🚀 빠른 시작

### 설치
```bash
npm install
```

### 사용 예제
```javascript
import { CodeQualityAnalyzer } from './phase9/ai-code-reviewer.js';
import { DocumentationGenerator } from './phase9/ai-documentation.js';
import { RefactoringEngine } from './phase9/ai-refactoring.js';
import { SecurityAnalyzer } from './phase9/ai-security-analyzer.js';
import { PerformanceProfiler } from './phase9/ai-performance-profiler.js';

const code = `
function process(data) {
  return data.map(x => x * 2).filter(x => x > 10);
}
`;

// 코드 리뷰
const reviewer = new CodeQualityAnalyzer();
console.log(reviewer.review(code));

// 문서 생성
const doc = new DocumentationGenerator();
console.log(doc.generateReadme(code));

// 리팩토링 제안
const engine = new RefactoringEngine();
console.log(engine.generateReport(code));

// 보안 분석
const security = new SecurityAnalyzer();
console.log(security.generateSecurityReport(code));

// 성능 분석
const perf = new PerformanceProfiler();
console.log(perf.generatePerformanceReport(code));
```

### 테스트 실행
```bash
node phase9/ai-code-reviewer.js
node phase9/ai-documentation.js
node phase9/ai-refactoring.js
node phase9/ai-security-analyzer.js
node phase9/ai-performance-profiler.js
```

